---
import { site } from "../config/site";

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-brand-950 text-brand-100">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent-500 text-white font-bold">G</span>
          <span class="text-base font-bold text-white tracking-tight">{site.name}</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-brand-200/80 leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          {site.tagline}
        </p>
        <div class="mt-7 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-medium text-brand-100">
          <span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent-400"></span>
          금융감독원 등록 보험대리점
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-300">Contact</h3>
        <dl class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <dt class="w-14 shrink-0 text-brand-300/70">전화</dt>
            <dd>
              <a href={site.contact.phoneHref} class="num font-semibold text-white hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors">
                {site.contact.phone}
              </a>
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <dt class="w-14 shrink-0 text-brand-300/70">이메일</dt>
            <dd><a href={`mailto:${site.contact.email}`} class="text-white hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors">{site.contact.email}</a></dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <dt class="w-14 shrink-0 text-brand-300/70">주소</dt>
            <dd class="text-brand-100/90 leading-relaxed">{site.contact.address}</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-300">Hours</h3>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-100/90">
          <li>{site.hours.weekday}</li>
          <li class="text-brand-200/60">{site.hours.lunch}</li>
          <li class="text-brand-200/60">{site.hours.weekend}</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-3 text-[11px] text-brand-300/60">
      <p class="space-x-2">
        <span>대표 {site.business.representative}</span>
        <span class="text-brand-300/30">|</span>
        <span class="num">사업자등록번호 {site.business.registrationNumber}</span>
        <span class="text-brand-300/30">|</span>
        <span class="num">보험대리점 {site.business.insuranceAgencyNumber}</span>
      </p>
      <p>&copy; {year} {site.name}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
